\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 Atmospheric perspective is quite subtle, due to the clean, dry air. Source of dire consequences for desert travelers who think the next watering hole isn\loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8217\'92t that far away.}
