\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 Large couds of dusta nd forest fire smoke rising above the crest of the santa catalina mountains and first thought it was an erupting volcano. Apparently , the fires were  ignited by falling boulders crashign together and cause sparks on the dry hillsides.  Geysers of water shot up from the floodplain, while other streams and springs throught hte region dried up or initiated flow. }
